metadata.name: "Patience" by daze #2
metadata.description: daze was the recipient of an artist grant from the Music Machines community. Their track “Patience” has been made exclusively available to the MM community for free. All royalties on secondary sales go directly back to daze. From the artist: "The first of 3 music NFTs. Collect all 3 for a surprise. These DnB tracks are the beginning of a new playground from the daze universe."
